g more than a convience class.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Everything used this class can be written from the public SDK.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It scrolls the text much like a teleprompter would with basic commands to pause and resume the scrolling.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The duration (speed) of the scrolling can be modified while scrolling by seting the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"duration"},{"type":"text","text":" property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It can support any language that the font supports."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If the content is not known up front, or subject to change, this is the utility class will not work (use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LiveText"},{"type":"text","text":" instance instead)."}]},"doc://ultralitesdk.UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK/ScrollLayout/AutoScroller/init(stringToScroll:duration:font:alignment:xOffset:width:height:)":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ultralitesdk.UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout\/AutoScroller\/init(stringToScroll:duration:font:alignment:xOffset:width:height:)","abstract":[{"text":"Auto Scrolls predined text","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"},{"kind":"text","text":"?("},{"text":"stringToScroll","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"duration","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"font"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UIFont","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIFont"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"alignment","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"