 are two supported modes: autoScroll on\/off"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When autoScroll is true, the slices are automatically scrolled.  Subscribe to the delgate and listen for the scrolled callback, when you get it send another slice of text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"When autoScroll is false, you can drive the slices and how they look on the screen.  You can send all the slices at once or send one at a time and animate it onto the screen at the current time.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout","role":"symbol"}}}